      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Central Vault Sync 0.1.12\n\nCommunity review candidate for revision-safe synchronization with a self-hosted WebObsidian server.\n\n### Highlights\n- Preserves local and server versions through revision-aware conflicts and deterministic clean text merges.\n- Flushes durable local work before pulling remote changes.\n- Handles immediate rename-then-modify echoes without replacing later local bytes.\n- Supports Markdown, binary attachments, rename/delete, offline recovery, and unsaved-editor protection.\n- Stores device credentials through Obsidian SecretStorage and includes no telemetry, ads, or remote code loading.\n\nUse a backed-up non-production vault while Community review and cross-platform validation are in progress.\n",
      "downloadCount": 4,
